---
title: Quick Crumbed Chicken & Lemony Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt & Slivered Almonds
description: A golden and crunchy crumb on chicken is the only way to eat chicken. It matches the bright and sunny couscous, tossed with
roast veggies and there’s a zap of zest in this bowl too. Everything is shining and golden tonight!
